OL,5, A former BBC radio presenter has been  
OL,6, found guilty of stalking four people   
OL,7, including broadcaster Jeremy Vine.     
OL,9,FHowever, Alex Belfield was found not   
OL,10,Fguilty of stalking four other people he
OL,11,Fwas accused of targeting.              
OL,13,FBelfield, who now runs a YouTube       
OL,14,Fchannel called The Voice of Reason,    
OL,15,Ftold jurors he had legitimate reasons  
OL,16,Ffor his online communications.         
OL,18,FThe 42-year-old, from Nottingham, is   
OL,19,Fdue to be sentenced on 16 September and
OL,20,Fhas been warned he could be jailed.    
